  . The 
  
    
      
        b
      
    
    {\displaystyle b}
   on the right-hand side can also be written as 
  
    
      
        
          b
          
            1
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle b^{1}}
  , giving 
  
    
      
        
          b
          
            r
            +
            r
          
        
