          b
          
            1
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle b^{r+r}=b^{1}}
  . Equating the exponents on both sides, we have 
  
    
      
        r
        +
        r
        =
        1
      
    
    {\displaystyle r+r=1}
  . Therefore, 
  
    
      
        r
        =
        
          
            1
            2
          
        
      
    
