            n
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle f(x)=cx^{n}}
   will also tend towards positive infinity with increasing 
  
    
      
        x
      
    
    {\displaystyle x}
  , but towards negative infinity with decreasing 
  
    
      
        x
      
    
    {\displaystyle x}
  . All graphs from the family of odd power functions have the general shape of 
  
    
      
        y
        =
        c
        
